data.description: Special assessment paid by seller at closing with excellent offer. Fantastic location, you'll love this renovated 2nd floor condo in popular Greenslake Condominiums. This is a  great 2 bedroom 2 bath 2nd floor unit has tile plank floors throughout, some modern finishes and new paint. This condo.has a screened-in porch balcony and a gas fireplace, Galley kitchen with granite counters and separate dining area. This is a peaceful community with a pool. Super cute and move in ready!
